snippet.title: Figment 2: Creed Valley - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Delve deep into a surreal world as you fight colorful enemies, solve puzzles, and battle through musical boss fights when Figment 2: Creed Valley comes to Nintendo Switch in Feb. 2022!

Download the demo today: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/figment-2-creed-valley-switch/

#Figment2 #IndieWorld #NintendoSwitch
